snippet.title: Official Call of Duty®: Black Ops III – Eclipse Multiplayer Trailer
snippet.description:
Eclipse, the second DLC map pack for Call of Duty®: Black Ops III, arrives first on PlayStation 4 on April 19, delivering four new action-packed Multiplayer maps, including the re-imagining of the Call of Duty: World at War classic, Banzai.

Battle through four new MP environments that take full advantage of the Black Ops III movement system, including a martial arts tournament arena, a post-apocalyptic tribal compound, a future civilian sub-orbital airport, and a military rail system suspended high above an active volcano.

Eclipse is available first on PlayStation 4 on April 19, 2016. Purchase the Call of Duty: Black Ops III Season Pass today: http://bit.ly/BO3SeasonPass
